summary:
Most people describe me as an energetic and social person. I have a lot of discipline, this is evident in my athletic and active lifestyle. I am always looking for new challenges, helping others by communicating well and sharing my passion. My passions include cooking, sports and music.

Engineering didn't interest me much as a child, but as I got older and went to high school, science subjects such as mathematics, physics and chemistry started to interest me more and more. After high school, I went to Windesheim. Here the mechanical engineering course appealed to me the most. In 2021 I graduated in mechanical engineering. Meanwhile, I am doing a Sales Traineeship, in which I currently fulfill the role of Junior Proposal Engineer. Here I can use my creativity and social skills.
